I"¸<ol>
  <li>Run command prompt (<code class="highlighter-rouge">cmd</code>, <strong>NOT</strong> <code class="highlighter-rouge">powershell</code>) as administrator.</li>
  <li>Install service:
    <pre><code class="language-ps">java -jar "%UserProfile%\Ubiquiti UniFi\lib\ace.jar" installsvc
</code></pre>
  </li>
  <li>Start service:
    <pre><code class="language-ps">java -jar "%UserProfile%\Ubiquiti UniFi\lib\ace.jar" startsvc
</code></pre>
  </li>
</ol>

